About

Tori Vaz

I'm Tori! This is my personal blog/little slice of the web for me to dump miscellaneous thoughts.

I love programming, writing, cooking and coming up with recipes, and video games. I like to dip my toes in a lot of different ponds and try lots of new things, so forgive me if I come across a little scattered :) At any rate, thanks for stopping by! Feel free to email me at victoriavaz24@gmail.com.
